        <p>Qure’s Micro-Infusion System has a one-two punch, making it uniquely effective.</p>
        <ol>
            <li>First, it uses tiny 24K gold needles (thinner than a hair) to gently press into your skin. This helps improve firmness and smooth out fine lines.</li>
