        <article>
            <h2>What you should know for the best results</h2>
            <p>The Qure Micro-Infusion System is designed with your safety in mind.</p>
            <p>Unlike popular at-home derma rollers, our stamper device features single-use sterile heads that help minimize the risk of infection or unnecessary skin damage caused by blunt and multi-use needles.</p>
            <p>Below are a few rules you should follow while using your Qure Micro-Infusion System:</p>
        </article>
        <div
            class="c-swiper"
            data-swiper='{
                "slidesPerView": 1.1,
